@startuml PrefixSharingArchitecture

title Prefix Sharing 完整架构图 (Current)

' ==================== Dependency 层 ====================
package "dependency/ (外部框架 - 侵入式修改)" as DependencyLayer #E3F2FD {

    ' ---- verl_v070 ----
    package "verl_v070/" as VerlPkg #BBDEFB {
        class "MegatronPPOActor" as MegatronPPOActor #90CAF9 {
            verl Megatron Actor
            PPO训练Actor，集成prefix sharing的micro-batch处理逻辑
            +forward_step()
            .. 负责单次 micro-batch 前向传播，调用 prefix sharing 准备和恢复 ..
            __关键修改 (所在函数)__
            +__init__(): Line 61-70 加入try/except
            .. 为了导入 prefix-sharing 模块，模块缺失时自动回退原始行为，不阻塞正常使用 ..
            +forward_step(): Line 585-593 插入 build_prefix_sharing_micro_batch()
            .. 在micro-batch内部，做前缀匹配、batch裁剪、生成 PrefixRuntimeState ..
            +forward_step(): Line 631-632 判断是否启用fused kernels
            ..当前不兼容融合算子，需要跑异常 ..
            +forward_step(): Line 680-681 插入 prefix_sharing_runtime_context()
            .. 为核心的forward_fn建立PrefixSharingRuntimeContext，传递PrefixSharingPlan、PrefixKVStore、LastRestoreSlots等 ..
            +forward_step()/logits_processor(): Line 669-675 插入 restore_suffix_first_log_probs_from_prefix()
            .. 用于logits_processor中 恢复 suffix第一个token的 logprob ..
        }
    }
    
    ' ---- megatron_v0150 ----
    package "megatron_v0150/" as MegatronPkg #C8E6C9 {
        class "SelfAttention" as SelfAttention #A5D6A7 {
            Megatron SelfAttention
            自注意力层，被patch以支持prefix sharing hook拦截
            +forward()
            .. 自注意力前向传播，QKV 计算后插入 prefix sharing hook ..
            __关键修改 (所在函数)__
            +forward()
            .. try/except 导入并调用 maybe_run_prefix_sharing_attention()，模块缺失时自动回退 ..
            +forward()
            .. 若 hook 成功，直接返回结果拦截原始逻辑 ..
            +forward()
            .. 原始 RoPE/Attention 逻辑，hook 失败时继续执行 ..
        }
    }
}

' ==================== Integration 层 ====================
package "prefix-sharing/integrations/ (框架适配层)" as IntegrationLayer #FFF3E0 {
    
    class "verl_mcore.py" as VerlMcore #FFCC80 {
        verl+mcore集成入口
        提供batch准备、logprob恢复、patch安装等集成函数
        +build_prefix_sharing_micro_batch()
        .. 前缀检测入口：配置验证 → 执行前缀复用计划 → batch 裁剪 → 构建 PrefixSharingRuntimeState ..
        +restore_suffix_first_log_probs_from_prefix()
        .. 恢复 reuser 的 suffix-first logprob，从 context 读取 restore_slots 并重新计算 ..
        +enable_prefix_sharing()
        .. 启用 prefix sharing：安装 Megatron attention patch ..
        +prefix_sharing_enabled()
        .. 上下文管理器包装 enable_prefix_sharing ..
    }
    
    class "verl_mcore.py\nPrefixSharingRuntimeState" as RuntimeState #FFCC80 {
        运行时状态容器
        封装执行计划、backend实例、packed runtime layout等运行时数据
        +prefix_sharing_plan: PrefixSharingPlan
        .. 执行计划，包含 reuse_specs、裁剪范围、restore specs 等 ..
        +backend: Any
        .. attention backend 实例，如 TorchReferenceBackend ..
        +packed_batch_layout: PackedBatchLayout
        .. 当前 forward 的真实 packed batch 布局，用于 RoPE、KV split 和 restore index ..
    }

    class "context.py\nPackedPrefixLastRestoreIndex" as PackedRestoreIndex #FFCC80 {
        Packed恢复索引
        在packed THD格式中定位prefix-last恢复位置
        +reuse_idx_in_batch: int
        +provider_idx_in_batch: int
        +provider_1d_pos: int
        +reuse_1d_pos: int
    }
    
    class "megatron_runtime.py" as MegatronRuntime #FFCC80 {
        Megatron运行时Hook
        拦截SelfAttention执行，完成RoPE、KV注入、Attention计算
        +maybe_run_prefix_sharing_attention()
        .. Attention 拦截执行核心：检查 context → 应用 RoPE → build_kv → attention → 返回结果 ..
        +_apply_positioned_rope()
        .. 应用保留的原始位置编码，处理非连续位置并利用 RoPE 线性特性外推扩展 ..
    }
    
    class "context.py" as Context #FFCC80 {
        运行时上下文管理器
        提供上下文管理器管理RuntimeContext生命周期
        +PrefixSharingRuntimeContext()
        .. 运行时上下文数据类，存储执行计划、PackedBatchLayout、KV Store、backend 和 restore index ..
        +prefix_sharing_runtime_context()
        .. 上下文管理器：创建 RuntimeContext → 设置 ContextVar → yield → 清理 store ..
        +current_prefix_sharing_context()
        .. 获取当前线程的 prefix sharing 上下文，供 Megatron attention hook 使用 ..
    }
}

' ==================== Core 层 ====================
package "prefix-sharing/core/ (核心语义层)" as CoreLayer #F3E5F5 {
    
    class "config.py\nPrefixSharingConfig" as Config #CE93D8 {
        配置管理器
        管理所有prefix sharing相关配置参数及验证
        +enable_prefix_sharing: bool
        +detector: str = "trie"
        +backend: str = "torch_ref"
        +min_prefix_len: int
        +min_group_size: int
        +boundary_strategy: str = "prefix_last_restore"
        +supported_pp_size: int = 1
        +supported_cp_size: int = 1
        +supported_rope_fusion: bool = False
        +supported_fused_qkv_rope: bool = False
        +validate_precision: bool = False
        +integrate_mode: str = "verl_megatron_actor"
        +model_type: str = "text_only_causal_lm"
        +validate()
        .. 配置验证，检查 phase 1 约束与框架兼容性 ..
    }
    
    class "prefix_detector.py\nPrefixDetector (ABC)" as Detector #CE93D8 {
        前缀检测器抽象基类
        定义检测可共享前缀的标准接口
        +{abstract} detect()
        .. 前缀检测抽象接口，输入 batch token IDs，输出 PrefixDetectionResult ..
    }
    
    class "prefix_detector.py\nTriePrefixDetector" as TrieDetector #CE93D8 {
        +detect()
        .. Trie 树检测入口，在线匹配最长公共前缀并输出复用关系 ..
    }
    
    class "prefix_detector.py\nPrefixDetectionResult" as DetectionResult #CE93D8 {
        前缀检测结果
        包含batch中所有样本的复用关系和分组信息
        +batch_size: int
        +reuse_specs: tuple[PrefixReuseSpec, ...]
        +groups: tuple[PrefixGroup, ...]
        +group_ids: tuple[int, ...]
        +provider_index: tuple[int, ...]
        +prefix_lens: tuple[int, ...]
        +is_provider: tuple[bool, ...]
    }
    
    class "prefix_detector.py\nPrefixGroup" as PrefixGroup #CE93D8 {
        前缀共享组
        共享相同前缀的一组样本及其元信息
        +group_id: int
        +member_indices: tuple[int, ...]
        +prefix_len: int
        +provider_index: int
    }
    
    class "planner.py\nPrefixSharingPlanner" as Planner #CE93D8 {
        规划器
        调用检测器检测可共享前缀，然后制定复用计划
        +config: PrefixSharingConfig
        +detector: TriePrefixDetector | None
        +plan()
        .. 执行规划入口，detect → plan_from_detection，生成 PrefixSharingPlan ..
        +plan_from_detection()
        .. 基于已有 PrefixDetectionResult 生成执行计划 ..
    }
    
    class "planner.py\nPrefixLastRestoreSpec" as RestoreSpec #CE93D8 {
        Prefix-Last恢复规范
        描述如何从provider恢复reuser的prefix-last位置logprob
        +reuse_idx_in_batch: int
        +provider_idx_in_batch: int
        +provider_prefix_last_pos: int
        +reuse_first_suffix_label_pos: int
        +output_slot: int
        +group_id: int
    }
    
    class "planner.py\nPrefixSharingPlan" as Plan #CE93D8 {
        前缀共享执行计划
        描述如何裁剪batch、复用KV、恢复logprob的完整方案
        +forward_id: int
        +micro_batch_id: int
        +batch_size: int
        +original_lengths: list[int]
        +reuse_specs: list[PrefixReuseSpec]
        +group_ids: list[int]
        +is_provider: list[bool]
        +provider_index: list[int]
        +prefix_lens: list[int]
        +suffix_lens: list[int]
        +kept_lengths_q: list[int]
        +expanded_lengths_kv: list[int]
        +cu_seqlens_q: list[int]
        +cu_seqlens_kv: list[int]
        +max_seqlen_q: int
        +max_seqlen_kv: int
        +q_position_offsets: list[int]
        +kv_position_offsets: list[int]
        +input_keep_ranges: list[Range]
        +label_keep_ranges: list[Range]
        +loss_mask_keep_ranges: list[Range]
        +prefix_last_restore: list[PrefixLastRestoreSpec]
        +has_sharing: property
        +is_reuser()
        +q_range_for_batch()
        +kv_range_for_batch()
        +restore_for_reuse()
    }
    
    class "prefix_detector.py\nPrefixReuseSpec" as ReuseSpec #CE93D8 {
        前缀复用规范
        描述reuser样本与provider的复用关系及prefix长度
        +reuse_idx_in_batch: int
        +provider_idx_in_batch: int
        +prefix_len: int
    }
    
    class "batch_trim.py\nTrimmedBatch" as TrimmedBatch #CE93D8 {
        裁剪后的batch
        保留suffix后的压缩batch结构
        +rows: list[list[T]]
        +flattened: list[T]
        +cu_seqlens: list[int]
    }
    
    class "batch_trim.py" as BatchTrim #CE93D8 {
        Batch裁剪模块
        根据执行计划裁剪batch，仅保留suffix部分
        +trim_batch()
        .. 通用裁剪函数，返回 TrimmedBatch ..
        +trim_inputs()
        .. 裁剪 input_ids，保留每个样本的 suffix ..
        +trim_labels()
        .. 裁剪 labels，对齐裁剪后的 input_ids ..
        +trim_loss_masks()
        .. 裁剪 loss mask ..
    }
    
    class "logprob.py" as Logprob #CE93D8 {
        Logprob恢复模块
        从provider恢复reuser的prefix-last位置logprob值
        +restore_prefix_last_logprobs()
        .. 组装包含 prefix-last 恢复语义的 response logprobs ..
        +build_provider_prefix_last_values()
        .. 从 provider 行收集 prefix-last 值 ..
        +compute_token_logprobs_from_logits()
        .. 从 logits 计算 token logprobs (需要 PyTorch) ..
        +restore_prefix_last_logprobs_tensor()
        .. 将恢复的 logprobs 插入填充的响应张量 ..
        +gather_provider_prefix_last_logits()
        .. 收集每个 reuse 样本的 provider prefix-last logits ..
    }
    
    class "prefix_store.py\nPrefixKVSlotId" as KVSlotId #CE93D8 {
        KV存储槽位标识
        唯一定位某层某样本的prefix KV缓存位置
        +forward_id: int
        +micro_batch_id: int
        +layer_id: int
        +sample_idx_in_batch: int
        +tp_rank: int
    }
    
    class "prefix_store.py\nStoredPrefixKV" as StoredKV #CE93D8 {
        存储的Prefix KV
        包含key/value张量及prefix长度的存储单元
        +key_tensor: Any
        +value_tensor: Any
        +prefix_len: int
    }
    
    class "prefix_store.py\nPrefixKVStore" as PrefixStore #CE93D8 {
        KV存储管理器
        管理provider的prefix KV写入和reuser的读取
        +store()
        .. 写入 provider 的 prefix KV，按复合 key 索引 ..
        +load()
        .. 读取 provider 的 prefix KV 供 reuser 注入 ..
        +contains()
        +clear()
        +close()
        .. 清理 KV cache，释放资源 ..
    }
}

' ==================== Backends 层 ====================
package "prefix-sharing/backends/ (硬件执行层)" as BackendsLayer #E8F5E9 {
    
    class "base.py\nPrefixAttentionBackend (Protocol)" as BackendProtocol #A5D6A7 {
        Attention Backend协议
        定义backend必须实现的RoPE、KV构建、Attention接口
        +capabilities: BackendCapabilities
        +validate()
        +apply_rope()
        +build_kv()
        +attention()
    }
    
    class "torch_ref.py\nTorchReferenceBackend" as TorchRef #A5D6A7 {
        PyTorch参考Backend
        用原生PyTorch实现attention计算，保留autograd
        +capabilities: BackendCapabilities
        +validate()
        .. 校验 backend 与 PrefixSharingConfig 兼容性 ..
        +apply_rope()
        .. 可选 RoPE 应用入口 ..
        +build_kv()
        .. provider 写入 KV 到 store，reuser 读取并拼接 prefix/suffix KV ..
        +attention()
        .. PyTorch 参考 attention 计算，保留 autograd 计算图支持梯度回传 ..
    }

    class "packed_layout.py\nPackedBatchLayout" as PackedLayout #A5D6A7 {
        Packed batch 布局
        描述 attention backend 看到的 packed tensor 坐标，不绑定 prefix-sharing 语义
        +valid_lengths: list[int]
        +padded_lengths: list[int]
        +cu_seqlens: list[int]
        +max_seqlen: int
        +packed_position_ids: Any
        +valid_token_mask: Any
        +from_valid_lengths()
        +from_kept_position_rows()
        +packed_index()
        +valid_slice()
    }
    
    class "cuda_ref.py\nCudaReferenceBackend" as CudaRef #A5D6A7 {
        CUDA参考Backend
        继承TorchReferenceBackend，Phase 1占位符
        .. 继承 TorchReferenceBackend，Phase 1 占位 ..
    }

    class "cann_ref.py\nCannReferenceBackend" as CannRef #A5D6A7 {
        CANN参考Backend
        继承TorchReferenceBackend，Phase 1占位符
        .. 继承 TorchReferenceBackend，Phase 1 占位 ..
    }
}

' ==================== 类继承关系 ====================
Detector <|-- TrieDetector : 实现
BackendProtocol <|.. TorchRef : 实现
TorchRef <|-- CudaRef : 继承
TorchRef <|-- CannRef : 继承

' ==================== Dependency -> Integration 调用 ====================
MegatronPPOActor ..> VerlMcore : 调用 build_prefix_sharing_micro_batch()
MegatronPPOActor ..> Context : 使用 prefix_sharing_runtime_context()
SelfAttention ..> MegatronRuntime : 调用 maybe_run_prefix_sharing_attention()

' ==================== Integration 内部依赖 ====================
VerlMcore ..> RuntimeState : 创建运行时状态
Context ..> RuntimeState : 使用构造 PrefixSharingRuntimeContext
RuntimeState *-- Plan : 持有执行计划
RuntimeState *-- PackedLayout : 持有 packed runtime 坐标

' ==================== Integration -> Core 调用 ====================
VerlMcore ..> Config : 读取/解析配置
VerlMcore ..> Planner : 生成执行计划
VerlMcore ..> Plan : 创建 PrefixSharingPlan
VerlMcore ..> BatchTrim : 裁剪 batch
VerlMcore ..> Logprob : 恢复 logprob
MegatronRuntime ..> Context : 获取 KV Store 和 Plan
MegatronRuntime ..> PackedLayout : 读取 packed_position_ids
MegatronRuntime ..> TorchRef : 执行 build_kv 和 attention

' ==================== Core 内部依赖 ====================
Planner *-- TrieDetector : 持有 detector
Planner ..> DetectionResult : plan_from_detection 输入
TrieDetector ..> DetectionResult : detect() 输出
DetectionResult *-- PrefixGroup : groups 字段
TrieDetector ..> ReuseSpec : 输出 reuse_specs
Planner ..> Plan : 生成 PrefixSharingPlan
Plan *-- ReuseSpec : reuse_specs
Plan *-- RestoreSpec : prefix_last_restore
BatchTrim ..> Plan : 使用裁剪范围
BatchTrim ..> TrimmedBatch : 返回裁剪结果
Logprob ..> Plan : 使用恢复位置
Context *-- PrefixStore : 持有 store
PrefixStore *-- StoredKV : entries 存储
PrefixStore ..> KVSlotId : 作为 key 使用

' ==================== Backend 依赖 ====================
TorchRef ..> Plan : 读取执行计划
TorchRef ..> PackedLayout : 按 padded/valid length 拆分 tensor
TorchRef ..> PrefixStore : 读写 KV

' ==================== 关键调用流程注释 ====================
note right of MegatronPPOActor
  **verl Actor 完整流程:**
  1. 准备 micro-batch
     → build_prefix_sharing_micro_batch()
  2. with prefix_sharing_runtime_context:
     → 进入 Megatron forward
  3. Megatron SelfAttention hook 拦截
  4. restore_suffix_first_log_probs_from_prefix()
  5. Context 退出自动清理
endnote

note right of SelfAttention
  **Megatron Attention Hook:**
  1. QKV 计算完成后
  2. try: maybe_run_prefix_sharing_attention()
  3. 成功: 直接返回结果
  4. 失败: 继续原始 RoPE/Attention
endnote

note bottom of Context
  **PrefixSharingRuntimeContext:**
  - prefix_sharing_plan: PrefixSharingPlan
  - packed_batch_layout: PackedBatchLayout
  - store: PrefixKVStore
  - backend: Any
  - prefix_last_restore_indices: packed 读写索引
  
  主入口是 prefix_sharing_runtime_context()
endnote

' ==================== 数据流 ====================
class "Input:\nMicro-batch\n(input_ids,\nattention_mask)" as Input #FFEBEE
class "Output:\nLogits / Loss\n/ Gradients" as Output #FFEBEE

Input ..> VerlMcore : 输入
TorchRef ..> Output : 输出

@enduml
